rchaeologist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"displacement\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her adolescent life and training came alongside a war that claimed the lives of more than 300,000 civilians over a ten-year period.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her adolescent life\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2213}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"a war\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"the lives\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 300,000 civilians\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"a ten-year period\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When a bomb dropped on a pool she was training in, she decided to flee to Europe.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bomb\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Almost ten years after her Mediterranean crossing, the number of refugees and displaced persons around the planet continues to grow.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her Mediterranean crossing\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"refugees\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"displaced persons\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The UNHCR expects to support 130 million forcibly displaced or stateless people in 2024.\", \"from\": 2542,