\": \"the shores\", \"from\": 4208, \"to\": 4218}, {\"ngram\": \"the Arabian Gulf\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4238}, {\"ngram\": \"her story\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4263}, {\"ngram\": \"a captivated boat\", \"from\": 4267, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"listeners\", \"from\": 4288, \"to\": 4297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after, she hurried to COP 2023 for yet another guest appearance.\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"COP\", \"from\": 4329, \"to\": 4332}, {\"ngram\": \"yet another guest appearance\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having met with world leaders likeBarack Obama, these high-profile speaking opportunities are now second nature to Yusra.\", \"from\": 4372, \"to\": 4493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4413, \"end\": 4418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama\", \"score\": 0.9941938646522712, \"rank\": 0.005840041775616583, \"text\": \"Obama\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama\"}, {\"begin\": 4487, \"end\": 4492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\", \"score\": 0.858682698055531, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yusra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"world leaders\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4401}, {\"ngram\": \"these high-profile speaking opportunities\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4461}, {\"ngram\": \"second nature\", \"from\": 4470, \"to\": 4483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But behind it all is a 25-year-old Syrian refugee who was forced to flee a home to which she was deeply connected.\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4529, \"end\": 4543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugees_of_the_Syrian_civil_war\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Syrian refugee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugees_of_the_Syrian_civil_war\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugees_of_the_Syrian_civil_war\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a home\", \"from\": 4567, \"to\": 4573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I look back, and I miss my country every day.\", \"from\": 4610, \"to\": 4656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I miss everything,\\\" she reflected.\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will forever say this looks like Syria\\u2026 It's just where I am from, and it will always be a part of me.\\\"\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4728, \"end\": 4733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\", \"score\": 0.9999972209654933, \"rank\": 2.779042114108129e-06, \"text\": \"Syria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Syrian_civil_war\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Knowing who you are is something very powerful,\\\" she added, emphasising the strength of her identity as a refugee, Olympian and advocate.\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4916, \"end\": 4924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0616258884071686e-13, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4833}, {\"ngram\": \"the strength\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4885}, {\"ngram\": \"her identity\", \"from\": 4889, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"advocate\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 4937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yusra shoulders a great responsibility by speaking for other refugees and admitted that she can sometimes \\\"get in her head\\\" about the legacy she wants to leave.\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 5100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4940, \"end\": 4945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\", \"score\": 0.858682698055531, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yusra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yusra_(archaeologist)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great responsibility\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 4978}, {\"ngram\": \"other refugees\", \"from\": 4995, \"to\": 5009}, {\"ngram\": \"her head\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5062}, {\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 5070, \"to\": 5080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I believe that I was very lucky, after competing at the Olympic Games twice for the Refugee Olympic Team, to have a voice,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 5102, \"to\": 5236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5187, \"end\": 5207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999721121640235, \"rank\": 2.7888613808397005e-05, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IOC_Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5155, \"to\": 5172}, {\"ngram\": \"a voice\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that so many refugees around the world cannot tell their stories and do not have the same platforms, so the more I share my stories, the more I am sharing more stories of refugees worldwide, so that's exactly why I do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many refugees\", \"from\": 