"from\": 5775, \"to\": 5791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But also you feel happy\\u2026 I achieved my dream of competing at the Olympics, and I will forever be the swimming girl.\\\"\", \"from\": 5804, \"to\": 5921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5866, \"to\": 5878}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming girl\", \"from\": 5902, \"to\": 5919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 5923, \"to\": 5980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate\", \"from\": 5923, \"to\": 5958}, {\"ngram\": \"All rights\", \"from\": 5959, \"to\": 5969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Associated Newspapers Limited.\", \"from\": 5981, \"to\": 6018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 5981, \"to\": 5982}]}]}"